[[File:KPF logo.svg|thumb|Logo of the Communist Platform]] The '''Communist Platform''' ({{lang-de|Kommunistische Plattform, KPF}}) is an association within the [[Left Party (Germany)|German Left Party]]. Among the main goals of the KPF are the preservation and advancement of Marxist thought, other goals are improving the situation of the poor and battling racism.<ref>[http://die-linke.de/partei/zusammenschluesse/kommunistische_plattform_der_partei_die_linke/ Homepage of the KPF on the website of the Left Party], retrieved at June 29th, 2009</ref> Its most prominent member is [[Sahra Wagenknecht]], who was a member of the European Parliament<ref>[http://www.europarl.europa.eu/members/public/geoSearch/view.do?language=EN&id=28250 Sahra Wagenknecht], Profile on the website of the European Parliament, retrieved at June 29th, 2009</ref> and is now a member of the Bundestag.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.linksfraktion.de/mdb_wagenknecht.php |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2009-11-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091103102931/http://www.linksfraktion.de/mdb_wagenknecht.php |archivedate=2009-11-03 |df= }}</ref> As of May 2008 the Platform had around 961 members <ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.verfassungsschutz.de/download/SHOW/vsbericht_2008_engl.pdf | title = Annual Report on the Protection of the Constitution 2008 | year = 2009 | publisher = Federal Office for the Protection of the Constitution | page = 144 | accessdate = 2010-09-26 | quote = Fn 122: KPF-Mitteilungen (KPF Bulletin), issue 12/2008, May 2008, p. 25. }}</ref>
In 2001 the association objected to a declaration made by the PDS, distancing itself from the building of the [[Berlin Wall]].<ref>Holger Kulick, [http://www.spiegel.de/politik/deutschland/0,1518,143009,00.html Gysi isoliert Kommunistische Plattform], Spiegel Online, July 2nd, 2001, retrieved at June 29th, 2009</ref>
Beside the activities within the party, the KPF cooperates with the [[German Communist Party]] (DKP).<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dkp-nordharz.de/vereinbarung_kpf_kpd_dkp.html |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2011-07-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718231355/http://www.dkp-nordharz.de/vereinbarung_kpf_kpd_dkp.html |archivedate=2011-07-18 |df= }}</ref>
