The '''University of Manitoba Students' Union Act''' is a [[Manitoba|Manitoban]] law defining the [[University of Manitoba Students' Union]].<ref>https://www.umsu.ca/governance/governing-documents</ref> The law has been in effect since November 1990.<ref>http://web2.gov.mb.ca/laws/statutes/private/c20390e.php</ref> UMSU is the only [[student government]] in Canada with its own specific law.
